#: .\robot_additions\40mm.json
msgid "40mm EMP grenade"
msgid_plural "40mm EMP grenades"
msgstr[0] "40毫米EMP手榴弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '40mm EMP grenade'}
#: .\robot_additions\40mm.json
msgid ""
"A 40mm grenade with an EMP charge.  It will release an electromagnetic pulse"
" capable of damaging robots and some equipment."
msgstr "一枚装有EMP装药的40毫米手榴弹。它会释放出能够损坏机器人和部分设备的电磁脉冲。"

#: .\robot_additions\40mm.json
msgid "active EMP grenade"
msgid_plural "active EMP grenades"
msgstr[0] "激活的EMP手榴弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'active EMP grenade'}
#: .\robot_additions\40mm.json
msgid ""
"This EMP grenade is active, and will shortly detonate, creating a large EMP "
"field that damages robots and drains bionic energy.  You may not want to be "
"holding it much longer."
msgstr "这枚EMP手榴弹已激活，即将爆炸，产生一个大型EMP场，损坏机器人并耗尽仿生能量。你或许不该再拿着它了。"

#: .\robot_additions\items.json
msgid "robot carrier"
msgid_plural "robot carriers"
msgstr[0] "机器人运载器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'robot carrier'}
#: .\robot_additions\items.json
msgid ""
"A heavy frame outfitted with tie-downs and attachment points for carrying "
"cargo, with additional railings to keep a large machine in place.  It is "
"meant to hold large drones and robots for transport.  Use it on a suitable "
"robot to capture, use it on an empty tile to release."
msgstr ""
"一个重型框架，配有系紧点和附件点用于承载货物，并带有额外的栏杆以固定大型机器。它旨在运输大型无人机和机器人。对合适的机器人使用以捕获，对空地块使用以释放。"

#: .\robot_additions\items.json
msgid "active glowball"
msgid_plural "active glowballs"
msgstr[0] "激活的发光球"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'active glowball'}.
#: .\robot_additions\items.json
msgid "The glowball goes dim."
msgstr "发光球变暗了。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'active glowball'}
#: .\robot_additions\items.json
msgid "A small plastic ball filled with glowing chemicals."
msgstr "一个装满发光化学品的小塑料球。"

#: .\robot_additions\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "robot dispatch center"
msgstr "机器人调度中心"

#: .\robot_additions\paintball.json
msgid "glowball"
msgid_plural "glowballs"
msgstr[0] "发光球"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'glowball'}
#: .\robot_additions\paintball.json
msgid ""
"A tube of small glowballs taken off the market due to hazardous chemicals.  "
"They deal virtually no damage, but light up on impact.  Useful for "
"illuminating an area without lighting up yourself in the process."
msgstr "一管因含有危险化学品而下市的小型发光球。它们几乎不造成伤害，但撞击时会发光。适用于照亮区域，同时避免在此过程中暴露自身。"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Robo-Hacker"
msgstr "机器人黑客"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Robo-Hacker"
msgstr "机器人黑客"

#. ~ Profession (male Robo-Hacker) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Before the end, your hobby was illegally reprogramming and repurposing "
"commercial robots, but you never thought your survival might depend on it."
msgstr "在末日降临前，你的爱好是非法重编程和改造商用机器人，但你从未想过自己的生存会依赖于此。"

#. ~ Profession (female Robo-Hacker) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Before the end, your hobby was illegally reprogramming and repurposing "
"commercial robots, but you never thought your survival might depend on it."
msgstr "在末日降临前，你的爱好是非法重编程和改造商用机器人，但你从未想过自己的生存会依赖于此。"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Robotics Engineer"
msgstr "机器人工程师"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Robotics Engineer"
msgstr "机器人工程师"

#. ~ Profession (male Robotics Engineer) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You were a low-level engineer at a robotics manufacturer.  The management "
"kept telling you putting flamethrowers on manhacks was 'unnecessary' and "
"'too dangerous,' but there's nothing to stop you now."
msgstr "你曾是机器人制造商的低级工程师。管理层一直告诉你，在追猎机器人上安装火焰喷射器是‘不必要的’且‘太危险’，但现在没什么能阻止你了。"

#. ~ Profession (female Robotics Engineer) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You were a low-level engineer at a robotics manufacturer.  The management "
"kept telling you putting flamethrowers on manhacks was 'unnecessary' and "
"'too dangerous,' but there's nothing to stop you now."
msgstr "你曾是机器人制造商的低级工程师。管理层一直告诉你，在追猎机器人上安装火焰喷射器是‘不必要的’且‘太危险’，但现在没什么能阻止你了。"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Robotics Prodigy"
msgstr "机器人天才"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Robotics Prodigy"
msgstr "机器人天才"

#. ~ Profession (male Robotics Prodigy) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've been building robots since you could hold a soldering iron, and you "
"don't intend to let the end of the world stop that from continuing."
msgstr "自从你能拿起烙铁起，你就一直在制造机器人，你不打算让世界末日阻止你继续下去。"

#. ~ Profession (female Robotics Prodigy) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You've been building robots since you could hold a soldering iron, and you "
"don't intend to let the end of the world stop that from continuing."
msgstr "自从你能拿起烙铁起，你就一直在制造机器人，你不打算让世界末日阻止你继续下去。"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Robot Adoptee"
msgstr "机器人收养者"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Robot Adoptee"
msgstr "机器人收养者"

#. ~ Profession (male Robot Adoptee) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"During the riots a military robot came out of nowhere to rescue you.  Maybe "
"it thinks you're someone important, who knows."
msgstr "在骚乱期间，一台军用机器人不知从何处出现并救了你。也许它认为你是什么重要人物，谁知道呢。"

#. ~ Profession (female Robot Adoptee) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"During the riots a military robot came out of nowhere to rescue you.  Maybe "
"it thinks you're someone important, who knows."
msgstr "在骚乱期间，一台军用机器人不知从何处出现并救了你。也许它认为你是什么重要人物，谁知道呢。"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Robo-hunter"
msgstr "机器人猎手"

#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Robo-hunter"
msgstr "机器人猎手"

#. ~ Profession (male Robo-hunter) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You paid a local hacker to build you a robotic hunting dog.  It's almost as "
"good as the real thing, but it doesn't respond well to being pet."
msgstr "你花钱请当地黑客为你造了一只机器猎犬。它几乎和真的一样好，但对抚摸反应不佳。"

#. ~ Profession (female Robo-hunter) description
#: .\robot_additions\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You paid a local hacker to build you a robotic hunting dog.  It's almost as "
"good as the real thing, but it doesn't respond well to being pet."
msgstr "你花钱请当地黑客为你造了一只机器猎犬。它几乎和真的一样好，但对抚摸反应不佳。"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Robots' for a male character
#: .\robot_additions\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Robots"
msgstr "机器人"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Robots' for a female character
#: .\robot_additions\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Robots"
msgstr "机器人"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Robots' for a male character.
#: .\robot_additions\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"During the riots and chaos, you hid in a robot dispatch center hoping the "
"robots would protect you, but they may prove more dangerous than the "
"zombies."
msgstr "在骚乱和混乱中，你躲进了一个机器人调度中心，希望机器人能保护你，但它们可能比僵尸更危险。"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Robots' for a female character.
#: .\robot_additions\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
msgid ""
"During the riots and chaos, you hid in a robot dispatch center hoping the "
"robots would protect you, but they may prove more dangerous than the "
"zombies."
msgstr "在骚乱和混乱中，你躲进了一个机器人调度中心，希望机器人能保护你，但它们可能比僵尸更危险。"

#. ~ Starting location for scenario 'Robots'.
#: .\robot_additions\scenarios.json
msgctxt "start_name"
msgid "In Town"
msgstr "在城镇中"

#: .\robot_additions\start_locations.json
msgid "Robot Dispatch Center"
msgstr "机器人调度中心"

#: .\robot_additions\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "robot_carrier"
msgstr "机器人运载器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'robot_carrier'}
#: .\robot_additions\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A cargo space for carrying robots.  'e'xamine it to capture a robot next to "
"you, or to release the robot currently contained.  When selecting a robot to"
" capture, choose its tile relative to you, not the part."
msgstr "用于装载机器人的货舱。按'e'键检查以捕获你旁边的机器人，或释放当前装载的机器人。选择捕获机器人时，请选择相对于你的格子，而不是部件。"

#: .\robot_additions\vehicles.json
msgid "Robotic Taxi"
msgstr "机器人出租车"

#: .\robot_additions\vehicles.json
msgid "Armored Robot Carrier"
msgstr "装甲机器人运载车"

#: .\robot_additions\vehicles.json
msgid "Humvee"
msgstr "悍马车"

#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json .\robot_workbench\items.json
msgid "Stationary CraftBuddy"
msgid_plural "Stationary CraftBuddys"
msgstr[0] "固定式工艺伙伴"

#. ~ Description for Stationary CraftBuddy
#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json
msgid ""
"A robot crafting assistant. Useable as stationary all-purpose craft station "
"and as workbench with great boost to work speed, also help you butcher "
"things near it. Unfolding it into stationary form produced some little "
"AutoPack section you can use to create some auto-crafting packets with "
"simple tasks. Can be dismantled retain it's portable form and functionality."
msgstr ""
"一个机器人制作助手。可用作固定的多功能制作站和工作台，大幅提升工作速度，还能帮助你处理附近的物品。展开为固定形态时，会产生一个小型自动包部分，可用于创建带有简单任务的自动制作包。可拆卸以保留其便携形态和功能。"

#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json
msgid "metal screeching!"
msgstr "金属尖啸声！"

#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json
msgid "clang!"
msgstr "哐当！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stationary CraftBuddy'}
#: .\robot_workbench\items.json
msgid ""
"This is a crafting_pseudo_item for craftbuddy bot functions and if you have "
"it as an separate item, something is wrong, WATCH OUT."
msgstr "这是用于工艺伙伴机器人功能的制作伪物品，如果你将其作为独立物品拥有，说明出了问题，请注意。"

#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack: mending rope to thread"
msgid_plural "AutoPack: mending rope to threads"
msgstr[0] "自动包：将绳索修补成线"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'AutoPack: mending rope to thread'}.
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack has finished it's production process."
msgstr "自动包已完成其生产过程。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'AutoPack: mending rope to thread'}.
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack didn't finished the task yet."
msgstr "自动包尚未完成任务。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'AutoPack: mending rope to thread'}
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid ""
"Packed automatic assembler that slowly but steadily produce many threads "
"from single rope. Requires assembled and installed stationary CraftBuddy "
"station nearby and some UPS to be packed. Activate it when it's done."
msgstr "打包的自动组装器，能缓慢但稳定地从单根绳索生产大量线。需要附近有组装并安装好的固定式工艺伙伴站和一些UPS电源才能打包。完成后激活它。"

#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack with threads from a single long rope"
msgid_plural "AutoPack with threads from a single long ropes"
msgstr[0] "自动包：从单根长绳索生产线"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'AutoPack with threads from a single long rope'}
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid ""
"A inactive AutoPack that finished it's work and disassembled single long "
"rope into large units of thread."
msgstr "一个已停用的自动包，完成了工作并将单根长绳索分解为大量线单位。"
